#: ../../source/janim/render/renderer_video.rst:2
msgid "renderer_video"
msgstr "renderer_video"

#: janim.render.renderer_video.VideoReader.time_to_pts:1 of
msgid "将实际时间转换为视频流时间戳"
msgstr "Convert the actual time to the video stream timestamp"

#: janim.render.renderer_video.VideoReader.ensure_frames_correct:1 of
msgid ""
"保证 ``pts`` 一定满足 ``frames[-2].pts <= pts < frames[-1].pts`` - 如果 ``pts`` 处于已解码区域的后面，但是没有超出太多"
"（由 ``self.pts_tolerance`` 决定），则让已解码区域逐渐后挪 - 如果 ``pts`` 处于已解码区域的前面，或处于后面超出太多，则 "
"``seek`` 重新构建已解码区域"
msgstr ""
"Ensure that ``pts`` always satisfies ``frames[-2].pts <= pts < frames[-1].pts`` - If ``pts`` is slightly after the "
"decoded region (within the tolerance defined by ``self.pts_tolerance``), gradually move the decoded region forward - If "
"``pts`` is before the decoded region, or is too far beyond it, perform a ``seek`` to rebuild the decoded region"
